{
  "stem": "22836.2",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And every morning, we have to go to work.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, everything, walk, walk.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, no, no driving-- none-- walking.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And walking, we was walking on-- not on-- not on the sidewalk-- where the horses, where the-- where the wagons going.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then everybody is looking at us.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, where-- we went-- from Osowa to Kostopol it was, let's see-- like two hours ride with horses-- two hours ride-- no, two hour-- one hour with a car.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, no.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We walk one time to stay there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they keep us four weeks there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And after that, we walk back home, yeah.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Back-- back to Osowa.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then, we always thinking they wouldn't bother us-- work, not work, we cutting in the wood, the-- the trees.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Everything we give it in along we can be survive-- be alive.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Over there, then they come in.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Some day they come in, and they took us all together.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The German with Ukraines-- it was a lot.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, everybody have to get out from their houses.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they-- and they keep us walking to Kostopol, to that-- like in that-- in that way.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Like we gone.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Then we-- we-- we lucky.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We-- we-- we run away, like, we was-- our house was the last one in that Osowa-- the last house.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And right away, was the woods-- but ours.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And when we hear that, we don't do nothing.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We went out, and we ran away.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we lucky.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We-- we lucky we ran out, that time.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And the rest, everybody take them away.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "A lot run away, and a lot they killed.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And so-- so it's finish.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It was finished.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "It was over.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We was not with them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, they killed.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You didn't have to see.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Anybody was killed.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
